{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/zoomd7fxe6gefrzd/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":null},"pageContext":{"url":"posts/zoomd7fxe6gefrzd","relativePath":"posts/zoomd7fxe6gefrzd","frontmatter":{"title":"Dance in the moment","stackbit_url_path":"posts/zoomd7fxe6gefrzd","date":"2022-12-12T15:28:03","excerpt":"","tags":[],"categories":[],"template":"post"},"html":"<p>今天和同事聊天，聊到了《明朝那些事儿》，聊到了朱元璋，他小时候被元朝官兵欺负，恨透了官僚，后来竟扭转乾坤，换了天地。</p>\n<p>做了皇帝，仍然勤奋努力，虽然如此，却到头来还是活成了他本来讨厌的样子……</p>\n<p>又想起最近，马斯克入主推特，也是搞得翻天地覆。其实，从他的行为来看，就是在摧毁推特的官僚系统。</p>\n<p>从程序员的视角来说，我还挺喜欢他的做法。我总觉得，公司只需要有实际干活的人就行，管理层，尤其是中层管理，不仅不带来价值，甚至是拖后腿的。</p>\n<p>我也曾在某小厂担任过这种所谓“二管”，但是当时其实仍然坚持 50% 以上的写代码时间，就是坚持只有在一线，才能真正创造价值。</p>\n<p>但一直想不通，为什么几乎所有公司都仍然有一个庞大的管理层呢？</p>\n<p>优秀的员工是不需要管理的，优秀的程序员更是不能管理，否则只是限制了其生产力啊。所以，之所以有庞大的官僚系统，是因为多数程序员其实不合格，多数员工都是打酱油吗？</p>\n<p>如果是这样，为什么连谷歌都不能免俗呢？</p>\n<p>我想像中的公司，不需要太多管理者，只需要极少的主持人，或者指挥家就行了。感觉马斯克在推特所推行的，就很类似这种理想公司的方向呀。</p>\n<p>但也不全是。做底层员工角度，票求签奋斗者协议之类的，就过分了。</p>\n<p>理想的公司，应该是充分解放生产力的。但现实情况，却恰恰相反。</p>\n<p>最近听说了亚马逊的 bar raiser 机制，大受震撼。也许，所谓的解放生产力，只是狭隘的纯业务视角。也许，只是格局没有打开。</p>\n<p>那么，那些格局打开了的人，究竟在想些什么呢？</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7c7b8616b910469ee12006a8c0d3d4f0/9568a/1670858350700-6bdf7703-fca2-4b2a-a7b9-5fa0e3304403.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.1081081081081%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"IMG_2815.jpeg\"\n        title=\"IMG_2815.jpeg\"\n        src=\"/static/7c7b8616b910469ee12006a8c0d3d4f0/1c72d/1670858350700-6bdf7703-fca2-4b2a-a7b9-5fa0e3304403.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7c7b8616b910469ee12006a8c0d3d4f0/a80bd/1670858350700-6bdf7703-fca2-4b2a-a7b9-5fa0e3304403.jpg 148w,\n/static/7c7b8616b910469ee12006a8c0d3d4f0/1c91a/1670858350700-6bdf7703-fca2-4b2a-a7b9-5fa0e3304403.jpg 295w,\n/static/7c7b8616b910469ee12006a8c0d3d4f0/1c72d/1670858350700-6bdf7703-fca2-4b2a-a7b9-5fa0e3304403.jpg 590w,\n/static/7c7b8616b910469ee12006a8c0d3d4f0/a8a14/1670858350700-6bdf7703-fca2-4b2a-a7b9-5fa0e3304403.jpg 885w,\n/static/7c7b8616b910469ee12006a8c0d3d4f0/fbd2c/1670858350700-6bdf7703-fca2-4b2a-a7b9-5fa0e3304403.jpg 1180w,\n/static/7c7b8616b910469ee12006a8c0d3d4f0/9568a/1670858350700-6bdf7703-fca2-4b2a-a7b9-5fa0e3304403.jpg 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>令我不解的官僚怪象，和前领导聊过，得到的回复耐人寻味，一直在琢磨： dance in the moment。</p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","author":"@zizhujy","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"About","url":"/about","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"关于","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/about","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"Contact","url":"/contact","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"Support Me","url":"